    • Brightness, Color Temperature & RGBWW AdjustableThe Smart recessed lighting 6 inch lets you adjust the color temperature from 2700K to 6500K. Brightness can be adjusted from 1% to 100%. With 16 million colors, you can freely change your lighting. The LED Recessed Lighting also features 8 modes to help you relax after a long day, highlighting the charm of an LED recessed ceiling light
    • WIFI & Bluetooth Dual ControlThe Canless LED recessed light supports both WIFI and Bluetooth connections, giving you more convenience and flexibility. Whether you're home or away, you can remotely control these recessed lights, eliminating the worry of leaving lights on and wasting energy.BESTECCT smart led recessed lighting 6 inch is compatible with Alexa and Google Assistant.NOTE: Only support 2.4 GHz Wi-Fi
    • Group ControlWith the group control feature, you can efficiently manage multiple smart lights at once. You can also create separate groups for different rooms, such as the living room, kitchen, bedroom, gaming room, and soffit,allowing you to adjust the smart recessed lighting and LED ceiling lights individually
    • Sync with Music & Multi Scene ModesBESTECCT color changing lights can sync with your music and react to game sounds, displaying different light colors to create various amazing atmospheres. Multiple scene modes allow you to choose the perfect setting based on your mood
    • APP Intelligent Control&Service:1.Open the "Surplife" app and tap "Add Device" or "+". 2.Keep your phone close to the device; it will search automatically.3.Select the device, connect to your network, and wait.4.Name the device, assign it to a room,and tap"Finish."Tip:Only Support 2.4 GHz WiFi frequency band signal. App also has features to help resolve any issues you encounter
    • Easy Installation & Superior QualityWith 12W (1100LM) output and a high CRI of 90+, this light is lightweight, slim, flicker-free, silent, and has a quick start-up. It comes with a junction box for easy installationjust connect the box to the cable and secure it to the ceiling using the spring clips
